{"tid":732130,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我老母喺度慢性自殺緊 我可以點做？","createTime":"2018-07-06T18:01:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T06:32:44.000Z","uid":79651,"like":5,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"90a61d42487946eab1e0f14f52eab4b94913efab","tid":732130,"uid":79651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T18:01:44.000Z","msg":"簡單講吓背景資料。是咁的，我老母本身都已經有糖尿、高血壓、肥胖問題，退咗休之後，垃圾嘅生活習慣令佢身體愈嚟愈差。佢依家日日都坐喺梳化睇CCTVB嘅劇，又唔願運動，搞到愈嚟愈肥。晚晚2點幾先瞓，朝早12點先起身，夜瞓嘅原因係因為睇錄影咗嘅劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n心肺功能極差，行路快少少都喘氣又標晒汗。無數次同佢講咁樣唔掂，叫佢運動吓。冬天嫌凍，夏天嫌熱。勸又勸過，逼又逼過，佢都唔聽人講，話「算啦，幾廿歲人仲減咩肥，我好enjoy依家嘅生活」 <br />\n<br />\n已經心裡有底佢隨時心臟病或者中風各樣，想問吓我應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2e282336f25f46522ae2679c3832b736cfc717","tid":732130,"uid":79651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T18:03:20.000Z","msg":"有無人入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86bd33446af2ad2de080d16c177808c3df1a2c27","tid":732130,"uid":79651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T18:04:41.000Z","msg":"人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a5fb652b14942363cc8fbaec668ce2c325f86d","tid":732130,"uid":79651,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T18:06:39.000Z","msg":"負評我做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4615c8ada8b16cd2902172f9e567edf523ab00d","tid":732130,"uid":90995,"like":49,"dislike":4,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T18:06:58.000Z","msg":"香港有邊個唔係慢性自殺緊"},{"pid":"826c2b04b5c432d89bd2b82ad01afcf0691e2614","tid":732130,"uid":27961,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T18:09:40.000Z","msg":"識朋友介紹佢去 搵興趣 跳大媽舞"},{"pid":"c416700f86e41492b370f3dbafef436cb9fe67ff","tid":732130,"uid":81505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed2e282336f25f46522ae2679c3832b736cfc7